HEADWORD: Peltry
<hw>Pelt"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>pelleterie</ets> peltry, furriery, fr. <ets>pelletier</ets> a
furrier, fr. OF. <ets>pel</ets> skin, F. <ets>peau</ets>, L.
<ets>pelis</ets>. See <er>Pelt</er> a skin, <er>Pell</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, <er>Fell</er> a skin.]</ety> <def>Pelts or skins,
collectively; skins with the fur on them; furs.</def>⟦br⟧
